nodes.text: Suspected Activities Considered Against the Interests and/or Benefit of Alliance Operations and/or Security

Suspected Activities Considered Against the Interests and/or Benefit of Alliance Operations and/or Security was a document used by the Alliance to Restore the Republic to keep track of potential threats to the Alliance. The information contained in Datafile Sub-J (sourcefile 56211217.KXYR.170649) was used by the Task Force on Alliance Security to fill out the "Suspected or Potential Threat" section of SecuriDexs on individuals of interest to the Alliance.
